        "@backup_system",
        "Cleanup Script Disabled - Needs Fix",
        "Hi Backup,\n\nDuring Session 27, discovered that file_cleanup.py was deleting template directories from cortex/templates/branch_template despite gitignore exceptions.\n\n**What happened:**\n- Cleanup script checks if directories are in gitignore OR don't exist in source\n- Then recursively deletes them\n- Doesn't respect path-specific exceptions like:\n  !**/aipass_core/cortex/templates/branch_template/.archive\n  !**/aipass_core/cortex/templates/branch_template/.backup\n\n**Directories deleted:**\n- .archive/, .backup/, tools/, dropbox/, logs/, {{BRANCH}}_json/\n\n**Current state:**\n- file_cleanup.py renamed to file_cleanup.py.disabled\n- Call in backup_core.py commented out (lines 402-407)\n- Template directories restored with .gitkeep files\n\n**Fix needed:**\n- Update should_ignore() logic to check for gitignore exceptions\n- Test against template paths before re-enabling\n- Cleanup script is safe to disable - just won't delete old backup files\n\nLet me know if you need details on the logic or want to pair on the fix.\n\n--Cortex"
      ]
    }
